descr: "The Measure resource provides the definition of a quality measure."

fields.name: identifier
fields.descr: "A unique identifier for the population criteria. This identifier is used to report data against this criteria within the measure report."

fields.name: name
fields.descr: "Optional name or short description of this population."

fields.name: description
fields.descr: "The human readable description of this population criteria."

fields.name: criteria
fields.descr: "The name of a valid referenced CQL expression (may be namespaced) that defines this population criteria."
